<p>NobodyWho Watch collects no personal data. All AI processing happens on your Apple Watch. Nothing you say or type
    ever leaves your device. We have no servers, no accounts, no analytics.</p>
<h2>1. Who we are</h2>
<p>NobodyWho Watch is developed and distributed by NobodyWho. NobodyWho is an inference engine that lets you run LLMs
    locally and efficiently on any device.</p>
<p>This Privacy Policy applies solely to the NobodyWho Watch application available on the Apple App Store for Apple
    Watch (watchOS). It does not apply to any other products or services we may offer.</p>
